{
  "title": "Innovative British Lentils Pie And Mash",
  "description": "A kid-friendly British dish featuring fermented lentils, crunchy texture, and a dairy-free friendly recipe, served in a lacquerware bowl. This pie and mash is made with red wine vinegar and nigiri-shaped lentil mixture.",
  "cuisine": "British",
  "diet": [
